User Story:
  Users should be able to:
    Add a DVD or Book to their personal library
    Access their personal library
    Edit information about a DVD or Book
    Delete a DVD or Book
    See if a DVD or Book is a hard copy or digital or both
    Search DVDs and Books
    Share their list with others?


Users
  Name
  Email
  Password
  has_many :dvds
  has_many :books

DVD
  Title
  Year Released (handled by external API?)
  Description (handled by external API?)
  Image (handled by external API?)
  belongs_to :user

Book
  Title (handled by external API?)
  Author (handled by external API?)
  Description (handled by external API?)
  Image (handled by external API?)
  belongs_to :user
